OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy across much of the
OL,6,Fnorthwest of the UK with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, which could be heavy at times
OL,8,Fand accompanied by blustery winds.
OL,9,FDrier and brighter further southeast,
OL,10,Fwith some pleasant spells of sunshine
OL,11,Fdeveloping. Feeling warmer here.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain will move southeastwards
OL,14,Facross the country through tonight,
OL,15,Fturning heavy in the north and west
OL,16,Fand accompanied by some rather gusty
OL,17,Fwinds. Showers following across
OL,18,FScotland and Northern Ireland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
