OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FRain will continue to move
OL,6,Facross southern and eastern England,
OL,7,Fagain turning heavy at times. Brighter
OL,8,Felsewhere, with a mixture of sunny
OL,9,Fspells and scattered showers. Feeling
OL,10,Frather fresh.
